snippet.title: Pakistan JIT Holds India Responsible for Pathankot Attack

localized.description:
Pathankot Terror Attack: Pakistan alleged that India killed its NIA officer Mohammed Tanzil Ahmed to cover up Pathankot terror attack. After Pak's allegations, India should find different ways to probe Pathankot attack: Defence Expert
